title: Odell's New Deal, Donald's Holdout, and Wentz's Return | GM Street (Ep. 288)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Odell Beckham Jr.'s new deal in New York, Aaron Donald's holdout and the Rams' preseason plan, Carson Wentz's Week 1 status, and Week 3 preseason thoughts.
